snippet.title: MVCIB Direct, Coming 10.23.2024 | Marvel vs. Capcom: Infinite & Beyond
snippet.description:
Tomorrow, we go Beyond. 

Tune in to Maximillian Dood's streaming channels tomorrow, October 23 @ 8PM PT for the latest updates to to Marvel vs. Capcom: Infinite & Beyond. You won't want to miss it!
